  "title": "LEGAL SECRETARY",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>AGP Law LLC is a Singapore-based full-service law firm that provides legal services to a diverse range of clients including MNCs, SGX listed entities, and SMEs.  We provide excellent service levels and value-added solutions. The firm has a strong reputation in the legal industry. The firm provides a positive work environment. We offer attractive remuneration packages including competitive salaries, fixed and variable bonuses.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist and work with solicitor(s);</li>\n  <li>Full secretarial support in preparation of correspondence and legal documents;</li>\n  <li>Other administrative support.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good command of written and spoken English;</li>\n  <li>Willing to work beyond office hours when required;</li>\n  <li>Meticulous, well organized and able to work under time constraints;</li>\n  <li>Motivated, pro-active and able to work in a team;</li>\n  <li>Good working knowledge of Microsoft Word, Excel and Outlook;</li>\n  <li>Minimum working experience of 1 to 2 years is preferred. Prepared to consider suitable candidates with less      experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Interested applicants are to send their resume stating current/ expected salaries to hr@agp.com.sg.</strong></p>",
